Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:13.14,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}五光十色 明滅可見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:21.27,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}時有風雨 時有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:25.36,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}我們卻望而止步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:31.11,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}若是能克服苦難的話
Comment: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.74,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}That’s Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.41,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}睜開眼的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:40.46,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}Brand New Story正要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:44.83,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}向前踏出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:49.01,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fax-0.2}為你開拓前方
